SIMPLE: whereon
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whereon
<hw>Where*on"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>On which; -- used relatively; <as>as, the earth
<ex>whereon</ex> we live</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>O fair foundation laid <qex>whereon</qex> to build.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>On what; -- used interrogatively; as,
<xex>whereon</xex> do we stand?</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whereout</ent>⟦br⟧
